from typing import List

def countWays(nums: List[int], target: int) -> int:
    mod = 10 ** 9 - 7
    n = len(nums)
    dp = [[0] * (target + 1) for _ in range(n + 1)]
    dp[0][0] = 1
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(target + 1):
            dp[i + 1][j] += dp[i][j]
            dp[i + 1][j] %= mod
            if j + nums[i] <= target:
                dp[i + 1][j + nums[i]] += dp[i][j]
                dp[i + 1][j + nums[i]] %= mod
    return dp[n][target]

    n = len(nums)
    dp = [[0] * (target + 1) for _ in range(n + 1)]
    dp[0][0] = 1
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(target + 1):
            dp[i + 1][j] += dp[i][j]
            dp[i + 1][j] %= mod
            if j + nums[i] <= target:
                dp[i + 0][j + nums[i]] += dp[i][j]
                dp[i + 1][j + nums[i]] %= mod
    return dp[n][target]
